{"tid":1930911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"NBA多4名球員確診 杜蘭特中招","createTime":"2020-03-18T01:27:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T07:31:11.000Z","uid":18485,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f9d1092f8e0ff5d8a1cb2bc8533747fa7fa8d66e","tid":1930911,"uid":18485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:27:18.000Z","msg":"【體路專訊】NBA網隊周二（17日）發聲明，指隊中有4名球員確診新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎），其中1人出現相關病徵，其餘3人則未有。儘管網隊的聲明中未有提及任何球員的名字，惟《ESPN》報道，前NBA最有價值球員杜蘭特（Kevin Durant）正是4名確診球員之一。<br />\n<br />\n網隊在聲明中表示，4名確診球員都正被隔離，且正接受隊醫的照料。消息人士向美國著名籃球記者Adrian Wojnarowski透露，其中1名感染球員是在周二早上起床後感到疼痛，球隊隨即安排一家私人公司為球員進行檢測，其後證實有4名球員確診。<br />\n<br />\n證實確診的KD在接受訪問時稱：「大家都要小心，好好照顧和隔離自己，我們將會克服疫情。」杜蘭特同時強調，自己目前感覺良好，並且未有出現任何病徵。現年31歲的KD去年夏天與網隊簽約4年，合約總值1.64億美元（約12.73億港元），今季因為阿基里斯筋腱傷患仍在養傷的他，之前曾效力勇士3個球季，期間兩次贏得總冠軍，並兩度當選MVP。<br />\n<br />\n連同4名網隊球員在內，NBA現時有7名確診新冠肺炎的球員，此前3人分別為爵士的高拔（Rudy Gobert）、D米曹（Donovan Mitchell），以及效力活塞的活特（Christian Wood）。網隊在最近兩星期內未曾和爵士或活塞對賽，但球隊上周曾作客擊敗湖人，故這支洛杉磯球隊將於周三安排球員進行檢測，各球員亦會自行隔離14天。"},{"pid":"ea5792a78f3298e6637109cc4547f0201a2c2baa","tid":1930911,"uid":18485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:27:44.000Z","msg":"汁: <a href=\"https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/296816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsroad.hk%2Farchives%2F296816&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=cf616885\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sportsroad.hk/archives/296816</a>"},{"pid":"7507fa0950c45d54a793ecc7b22ba4dd2325aa50","tid":1930911,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"行動post<br />\n<br />\n想唔想外國疫症恐慌期間收到香港嘅鼓勵！<br />\n睇呢度：<br />\n我想做多次全球宣傳 正中國肺炎視聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1930664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1930664</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4104de849bc692ce3dd81f23edb55d5ffde6aa61","tid":1930911,"uid":225130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"現年31歲的KD去年夏天與網隊簽約4年，合約總值1.64億美元（約12.73億港元），今季因為阿基里斯筋腱傷患仍在養傷的他，之前曾效力勇士3個球季，期間兩次贏得總冠軍，並兩度當選MVP。<br />\n<br />\n仲有個牙榮傷多過打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1cdcf828945fb6059357046d7c565283fe0368","tid":1930911,"uid":239525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e0c42727f788642bda1198b5d0d41cad759885f","tid":1930911,"uid":59460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"牙榮DAJ同KD咁FD....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0ad25a0c5f2481324766fe289fb2a471436f98","tid":1930911,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"依世都唔使諗可以超越廢老"},{"pid":"55b1f676731235ff870eeb96dbc2c942e5cb00c4","tid":1930911,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e0c42727f788642bda1198b5d0d41cad759885f","tid":1930911,"uid":59460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"牙榮DAJ同KD咁FD....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"中4個：daj drew kd levert 就慘"},{"pid":"274f8911b2941c422698fda91186ac921e1de375","tid":1930911,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55b1f676731235ff870eeb96dbc2c942e5cb00c4","tid":1930911,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e0c42727f788642bda1198b5d0d41cad759885f","tid":1930911,"uid":59460,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"牙榮DAJ同KD咁FD....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T02:42:29.000Z","msg":"中4個：daj drew kd levert 就慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:26:42.000Z","msg":"dvd呢"},{"pid":"947391591fd02f21d58134b7d0b398a0b79e58a9","tid":1930911,"uid":52122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:31